-md straight-corners:rounded-sm shadow-sm"><code id="«R14ld38ut1letrnb»" class="inline-grid min-w-full grid-cols-[auto_1fr] [count-reset:line] print:whitespace-pre-wrap"><span class="highlight-line"><span class="highlight-line-content">function createContext(config: ClientConfig): number {<!-- -->
